				h2 Skills
				.resume

					img.panel-3-overlay(src="public/dist/images/panel-3-overlay.png")

					h3.resume-html HTML 
					ul 
						li Experience writing semantic HTML5, as well as Jade.

					h3.resume-css CSS 
					ul
						li Experience with LESS, Stylus, Bootstrap, Semantic UI.

					h3.resume-js JS
					ul 
						li Experience writing javascript as well as using jQuery, Backbone, Angular, Node and configuring Grunt tasks.

